{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Design is not just about what people see, it’s also about what they hear. Learn about how sound design can help you create a more immersive, usable and meaningful user experience in your app or game, and get a glimpse of how the sounds in Apple products are created."}],"kind":"article","variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc17-803-designing-sound"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"metadata":{"role":"sampleCode","roleHeading":"WWDC17","modules":[{"name":"WWDC Notes"}],"title":"Designing Sound"},"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes","doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC17"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Overview","anchor":"overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"😱 “No Overview Available!”"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Be the hero to change that by watching the video and providing notes! It’s super easy:"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"identifier":"https:\/\/wwdcnotes.com\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/contributing","type":"reference","isActive":true}]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Related Sessions","anchor":"Related-Sessions"},{"type":"links","items":["doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC23-10271-Explore-immersive-sound-design","doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC19-223-Expanding-the-Sensory-Experience-with-Core-Haptics","doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC17-802-Essential-Design-Principles","doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC17-804-Designing-Across-Platforms"],"style":"list"}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC17-803-Designing-Sound","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"sampleCodeDownload":{"kind":"sampleDownload","action":{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/videos\/play\/wwdc2017\/803","overridingTitle":"Watch Video (34 min)"}},"references":{"doc://WWDCNotes/documentation/WWDCNotes/WWDC17":{"title":"WWDC17","type":"topic","role":"collectionGroup","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Xcode 9, Swift 4.0, iOS 11, macOS 10.13 (High Sierra), tvOS 11, watchOS 4."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"New APIs: "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Core NFC"},{"type":"text","text":" and more."}],"url":"\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc17","kind":"article","identifier":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC17","images":[{"type":"icon","identifier":"WWDC17-Icon.png"},{"type":"card","identifier":"WWDC17.jpeg"}]},"doc://WWDCNotes/documentation/WWDCNotes/WWDC17-802-Essential-Design-Principles":{"kind":"article","url":"\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc17-802-essential-design-principles","title":"Essential Design Principles","type":"topic","role":"sampleCode","identifier":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC17-802-Essential-Design-Principles","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Design principles are the key to understanding how design serves human needs for safety, meaning, achievement and beauty. Learn what these principles are and how they can help you design more welcoming, understandable, empowering and gratifying user experiences."}]},"WWDC17-Icon.png":{"variants":[{"url":"\/images\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC17-Icon.png","traits":["1x","light"]}],"type":"image","alt":null,"identifier":"WWDC17-Icon.png"},"https://wwdcnotes.com/documentation/wwdcnotes/contributing":{"titleInlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Learn More…"}],"url":"https:\/\/wwdcnotes.com\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/contributing","type":"link","title":"Learn More…","identifier":"https:\/\/wwdcnotes.com\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/contributing"},"doc://WWDCNotes/documentation/WWDCNotes":{"role":"collection","images":[{"identifier":"WWDCNotes.png","type":"icon"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Session notes shared by the community for the community."}],"type":"topic","title":"WWDC Notes","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/wwdcnotes","identifier":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes"},"doc://WWDCNotes/documentation/WWDCNotes/WWDC23-10271-Explore-immersive-sound-design":{"url":"\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc23-10271-explore-immersive-sound-design","identifier":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC23-10271-Explore-immersive-sound-design","title":"Explore immersive sound design","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Discover how you can use sound to enhance the experience of your visionOS apps and games. Learn how Apple designers select sounds and build soundscapes to create textural, immersive experiences. We’ll share how you can enrich basic interactions in your app with sound when you place audio cues spatially, vary repetitive sounds, and build moments of sonic delight into your app."}],"type":"topic","role":"sampleCode","kind":"article"},"doc://WWDCNotes/documentation/WWDCNotes/WWDC19-223-Expanding-the-Sensory-Experience-with-Core-Haptics":{"role":"sampleCode","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Core Haptics lets you design your own haptics with synchronized audio on iPhone. In this two part session, learn essential sound and haptic design principles and concepts for creating meaningful and delightful experiences that engage a wider range of human senses. Discover how to combine visuals, audio and haptics, using the Taptic Engine, to add a new level of realism and improve feedback in your app or game. Understand how to create and play back content, and where Core Haptics fits in with other audio and haptic APIs."}],"type":"topic","title":"Expanding the Sensory Experience with Core Haptics","url":"\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc19-223-expanding-the-sensory-experience-with-core-haptics","kind":"article","identifier":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC19-223-Expanding-the-Sensory-Experience-with-Core-Haptics"},"WWDCNotes.png":{"variants":[{"traits":["1x","light"],"url":"\/images\/WWDCNotes\/WWDCNotes.png"}],"type":"image","identifier":"WWDCNotes.png","alt":null},"https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2017/803":{"url":"https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/videos\/play\/wwdc2017\/803","type":"download","checksum":null,"identifier":"https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/videos\/play\/wwdc2017\/803"},"WWDC17.jpeg":{"variants":[{"traits":["1x","light"],"url":"\/images\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC17.jpeg"}],"type":"image","alt":null,"identifier":"WWDC17.jpeg"},"doc://WWDCNotes/documentation/WWDCNotes/WWDC17-804-Designing-Across-Platforms":{"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc17-804-designing-across-platforms","kind":"article","identifier":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC17-804-Designing-Across-Platforms","role":"sampleCode","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Learn techniques for determining which Apple platforms are right for your app and how to create a great user experience by designing for the unique capabilities and strengths of each platform."}],"title":"Designing Across Platforms"}}}